>Description:
The collects/net/url-unit.ss file only includes the host name when
it sets the HTTP Host header in the http://getpost-impure-port
function. (See line 135)

According to RFC 2616, the port should be included as well when the
port is not 80.

http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec14.html
